low = -2
high = 2
opt = Optimizer([(low, high), (low, high)])
with pytest.raises(ValueError) as e:
    opt.tell([[low + 1], [low + 1, low + 2], [low + 1, low + 3]], 2.0)
assert 'dimensions as the space' in str(e.value)
with pytest.raises(ValueError) as e:
    opt.tell([[low + 1, low + 1, low + 1], [low + 1, low + 2], [low + 1, 
        low + 3]], 2.0)
assert 'dimensions as the space' in str(e.value)
